      <title>土耳其放宽银行强制购买政府债券的规定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/turkey-eases-rules-on-forced-bank-buying-of-government-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其进一步放宽了迫使银行购买政府债券的监管，并再次降低了安全维持比率，以结束对贷方的惩罚性措施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/turkey-eases-rules-on-forced-bank-buying-of-government-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 06:06:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>2024 年欧洲杯将帮助啤酒在今年夏天统治鸡尾酒</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/euro-2024-will-help-beer-reign-over-cocktails-this-summer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[全球最大的啤酒生产商希望今年夏天温暖的天气和重大体育赛事能够帮助他们从“残酷”的 2023 年中恢复过来——但烈酒制造商在未来几个月仍可能面临挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/euro-2024-will-help-beer-reign-over-cocktails-this-summer</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 06:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
