    <item>
      <title>印度寻求每年1000亿美元的外国直接投资以吸引中国套期保值者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/india-seeks-100-billion-a-year-in-fdi-as-it-woos-china-hedgers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位高级官员表示，印度的目标是每年吸引至少 1000 亿美元的外国直接投资总额，因为这个南亚国家正在吸引寻求除中国以外的多元化投资的投资者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/india-seeks-100-billion-a-year-in-fdi-as-it-woos-china-hedgers</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 02:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Edge：马来西亚机场可能在 GIP 股权出售之前私有化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/malaysia-airports-may-be-privatised-before-gip-stake-sale-edge</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《The Edge》援引未具名消息人士的报道称，马来西亚机场有限公司可能会在将股权出售给私募股权公司 Global Infrastructure Partners 之前由其主要股东私有化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/malaysia-airports-may-be-privatised-before-gip-stake-sale-edge</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 01:31:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>调查：通货膨胀仍然是菲律宾公民最关心的问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/inflation-is-top-worry-among-filipinos-poll</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项受到广泛关注的调查显示，通货膨胀仍然是菲律宾公民最紧迫的担忧，这是顽固的价格压力可能使政策制定者刺激经济增长的努力变得复杂化的最新迹象。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/inflation-is-top-worry-among-filipinos-poll</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 01:30:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>读卖新闻：日产因少付企业费用而没有资格享受税收减免</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/nissan-ineligible-for-tax-break-after-underpaying-firms-yomiuri</link>
      <description><![CDATA[《读卖新闻》称，日产汽车公司 (Nissan Motor Co.) 不再有资格享受支持提高工资的公司的税收减免，因为该汽车制造商少付了承包商约 30 亿日元（合 2,000 万美元）的费用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/nissan-ineligible-for-tax-break-after-underpaying-firms-yomiuri</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 01:12:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Ares、Blue Owl 为 Catalent 交易牵头 48 亿美元私人债务</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/ares-ares-blue-owl-lead-4-8-billion-private-debt-for-catalent-ctlt-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Ares Management Corp. 和 Blue Owl Capital Inc. 正在牵头一组私人信贷机构，为收购药品制造商 Catalent Inc. 提供 48 亿美元的债务融资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-05/ares-ares-blue-owl-lead-4-8-billion-private-debt-for-catalent-ctlt-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 05 Apr 2024 20:35:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
